Sentencas: Novel TiN-Ni cermets with high oxidation resistance and excellent electrical conductivity were developed and evaluated as intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs) interconnects.
Titulo: TiN-Ni Cermets with High Oxidation Resistance and Electrical Conductivity as Candidates for Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Interconnects
